name: Mysterious Unnamed Space Game
description:
You find yourself stranded in another galaxy. Can you and your 5 shipmates find a way back? What sorts of horrible fate awaits you so very far away from home?

A game made over a weekend for the Tojam Tentacular!

Game programming by Askiisoft, The Monster King and Francis Coulombe.

Dialogue written by Lurdiak.

Art by Lord Mo, Tunan Pan and Francis Coulombe.

Music composed by cBoyardee.
